The paper proposes a question answering model for the educational domain that incorporates educational semantics and preserves correlations between conceptual entities. This suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and education technology (cs.EDU).
